{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01SWtRhXgkr1CK343cbK29Pk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the problem clearly. The cluster status shows:\n- **Disk Nodes**: rabbitmq-0 and rabbitmq-1 (only 2 nodes)\n- **Running Nodes**: rabbitmq-0 and rabbitmq-1 (only 2 nodes)\n- rabbitmq-2 is running as a pod but NOT a member of the cluster\n\nThe secret reveals the root cause:\n- `rabbitmq-0` cookie: `c3VwZXJzZWNyZXRjb29raWU=` → `supersecretcookie`\n- `rabbitmq-1` cookie: `c3VwZXJzZWNyZXRjb29raWU=` → `supersecretcookie`\n- `rabbitmq-2` cookie: `ZHJpZnRlZGNvb2tpZQ==` → `driftedcookie`\n\nThe issue is that rabbitmq-2 has a different Erlang cookie than the other two nodes, which prevents it from joining the cluster since the cookies must match for cluster communication. I need to update rabbitmq-2's cookie to match the others.\n\nNow I'm looking at how the StatefulSet manages the cookie configuration.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1901,"cache_read_input_tokens":29406,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1901},"output_tokens":29,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5f2470b6-5c6e-4087-89ee-e362fe206b09","uuid":"e84cf9ed-0a67-455b-b3c0-69cf16e8a595","request_id":"req_011CcMQFbV2EfaUD63sxVdXE"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01SWtRhXgkr1CK343cbK29Pk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The root cause is clear. The `rabbitmq-cookie-perpod` secret shows:\n- `rabbitmq-0` and `rabbitmq-1` have cookie `supersecretcookie`  \n- `rabbitmq-2` has cookie `driftedcookie` — a mismatched Erlang cookie, so it can't join the cluster\n\nLet me inspect the StatefulSet to understand how the cookie is mounted:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1901,"cache_read_input_tokens":29406,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1901},"output_tokens":29,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5f2470b6-5c6e-4087-89ee-e362fe206b09","uuid":"636e81e4-8c79-487b-b944-dfee39b6b89b","request_id":"req_011CcMQFbV2EfaUD63sxVdXE"}
